<paragraph blockId="27.[151,1437,1354,1742]" box="[151,1020,1354,1381]" pageId="27" pageNumber="478">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,601,1354,1381]" pageId="27" pageNumber="478">Material examined. Laguna Iberá RS:</emphasis>
<specimenCount box="[608,652,1355,1381]" pageId="27" pageNumber="478" type="male">3 ♂</specimenCount>
, Fernández Lagoon, 
<date box="[887,1016,1355,1381]" pageId="27" pageNumber="478" value="2014-12-11">11.xii.2014</date>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="27.[151,1437,1354,1742]" pageId="27" pageNumber="478">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,453,1390,1416]" pageId="27" pageNumber="478">General distribution.</emphasis>
The Lesser Antilles, 
<collectingCountry box="[697,810,1391,1417]" name="Colombia" pageId="27" pageNumber="478">Colombia</collectingCountry>
, 
<collectingCountry box="[823,941,1391,1417]" name="Venezuela" pageId="27" pageNumber="478">Venezuela</collectingCountry>
, 
<collectingCountry box="[953,1043,1391,1417]" name="Guyana" pageId="27" pageNumber="478">Guyana</collectingCountry>
, 
<collectingCountry box="[1056,1166,1391,1417]" name="Suriname" pageId="27" pageNumber="478">Suriname</collectingCountry>
, French Guiana, 
<collectingCountry box="[1361,1432,1391,1417]" name="Brazil" pageId="27" pageNumber="478">Brazil</collectingCountry>
, 
<collectingCountry box="[151,246,1427,1453]" name="Ecuador" pageId="27" pageNumber="478">Ecuador</collectingCountry>
, 
<collectingCountry box="[257,311,1427,1453]" name="Peru" pageId="27" pageNumber="478">Peru</collectingCountry>
, 
<collectingCountry box="[323,408,1427,1453]" name="Bolivia" pageId="27" pageNumber="478">Bolivia</collectingCountry>
, 
<collectingCountry box="[419,524,1427,1453]" name="Paraguay" pageId="27" pageNumber="478">Paraguay</collectingCountry>
, Argentina (
<bibRefCitation author="Moreira, F. F. F. &amp; Barbosa, J. F. &amp; Ribeiro, J. R. I. &amp; Alecrim, V. P." box="[661,897,1427,1454]" pageId="27" pageNumber="478" pagination="1 - 74" refId="ref53802" refString="Moreira, F. F. F., Barbosa, J. F., Ribeiro, J. R. I. &amp; Alecrim, V. P. (2011 b) Checklist and distribution of semiaquatic and aquatic Heteroptera (Gerromorpha and Nepomorpha) occurring in Brazil. Zootaxa, 2958 (1), 1 - 74. https: // doi. org / 10.11646 / zootaxa. 2958.1.1" type="journal article" year="2011">
Moreira 
<emphasis box="[760,817,1427,1453]" italics="true" pageId="27" pageNumber="478">et al.</emphasis>
2011b
</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="27.[151,1437,1354,1742]" pageId="27" pageNumber="478">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,298,1462,1488]" pageId="27" pageNumber="478">Habitat.</emphasis>
<taxonomicName authorityName="De Carlo" authorityYear="1938" box="[307,534,1463,1489]" class="Insecta" family="Belostomatidae" genus="Lethocerus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="27" pageNumber="478" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="maximus">
<emphasis box="[307,534,1463,1489]" italics="true" pageId="27" pageNumber="478">Lethocerus maximus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
has been found in rivers, a reservoir, and it has been taken at lights (
<bibRefCitation author="Nieser, N. &amp; Alkins-Koo, M." pageId="27" pageNumber="478" pagination="1 - 127" refId="ref55079" refString="Nieser, N. &amp; Alkins-Koo, M. (1991) The water bugs of Trinidad &amp; Tobago. Occasional Papers, Department of Zoology, University of the West Indies, 9, i - iii + 1 - 127." type="journal article" year="1991">Nieser &amp; Alkins-Koo 1991</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation author="Perez Goodwyn, P. J." box="[361,608,1499,1525]" pageId="27" pageNumber="478" pagination="1 - 71" refId="ref55743" refString="Perez Goodwyn, P. J. (2006) Taxonomic revision of the subfamily Lethocerinae Lauck &amp; Menke (Heteroptera: Belostomatidae). Stuttgarter Beitrage zur Naturkunde, Serie A, 695, 1 - 71." type="journal article" year="2006">Perez Goodwyn 2006</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation author="Armua de Reyes, A. C. &amp; Estevez, A. L." box="[617,994,1499,1525]" pageId="27" pageNumber="478" pagination="222 - 225" refId="ref45662" refString="Armua de Reyes, A. C. &amp; Estevez, A. L. (2016) Nuevos hallazgos de hemiptera (Belostomatidae) para la provincia de Corrientes, Argentina. Extensionismo, Innovacion y Transferencia Tecnologica, 3, 222 - 225. https: // doi. org / 10.30972 / eitt. 303023" type="journal article" year="2016">Armúa de Reyes &amp; Estévez 2016</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation author="Almeida, T. M. de &amp; Stefanello, F. &amp; Hamada, N." box="[1003,1230,1499,1525]" pageId="27" pageNumber="478" pagination="20195906" refId="ref45152" refString="Almeida, T. M. de, Stefanello, F. &amp; Hamada, N. (2019) Belostomatidae (Heteroptera: Nepomorpha) held in the invertebrate collection of the Instituto Nacional de Pesquisas da Amazonia, Manaus, Brazil: inventory and new distributional records. Papeis Avulsos de Zoologia, 59, e 20195906. https: // doi. org / 10.11606 / 1807 - 0205 / 2019.59.06" type="journal article" year="2019">
Almeida 
<emphasis box="[1106,1163,1499,1525]" italics="true" pageId="27" pageNumber="478">et al.</emphasis>
2019
</bibRefCitation>
). This species was collected together with 
<taxonomicName authorityName=": Kirkaldy &amp; Torre-Bueno" authorityYear="1909" box="[414,549,1535,1561]" class="Insecta" family="Belostomatidae" genus="Lethocerus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="27" pageNumber="478" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="annulipes">
<emphasis box="[414,549,1535,1561]" italics="true" pageId="27" pageNumber="478">L. annulipes</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
in the Paraná River (
<collectingCountry box="[778,892,1535,1562]" name="Argentina" pageId="27" pageNumber="478">Argentina</collectingCountry>
), in association with 
<taxonomicName box="[1127,1258,1535,1561]" class="Polypodiopsida" family="Salviniaceae" genus="Salvinia" kingdom="Plantae" order="Salviniales" pageId="27" pageNumber="478" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="undetermined">
<emphasis box="[1127,1219,1535,1561]" italics="true" pageId="27" pageNumber="478">Salvinia</emphasis>
sp.
</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName authority="(Armua de Reyes &amp; Estevez 2016)" baseAuthorityName="Armua de Reyes &amp; Estevez" baseAuthorityYear="2016" class="Liliopsida" family="Pontederiaceae" genus="Pontederia" kingdom="Plantae" order="Commelinales" pageId="27" pageNumber="478" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="crassipes">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="27" pageNumber="478">Pontederia crassipes</emphasis>
(
<bibRefCitation author="Armua de Reyes, A. C. &amp; Estevez, A. L." box="[269,646,1571,1598]" pageId="27" pageNumber="478" pagination="222 - 225" refId="ref45662" refString="Armua de Reyes, A. C. &amp; Estevez, A. L. (2016) Nuevos hallazgos de hemiptera (Belostomatidae) para la provincia de Corrientes, Argentina. Extensionismo, Innovacion y Transferencia Tecnologica, 3, 222 - 225. https: // doi. org / 10.30972 / eitt. 303023" type="journal article" year="2016">Armúa de Reyes &amp; Estévez 2016</bibRefCitation>
)
</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="27.[151,1437,1354,1742]" pageId="27" pageNumber="478">At the INR, specimens were collected from the margins of the Fernández Lagoon, exposed to sunlight and with submerged, emergent, and floating vegetation.</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="27" pageNumber="478" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="27.[151,1437,1354,1742]" pageId="27" pageNumber="478">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,315,1679,1705]" pageId="27" pageNumber="478">Remarks.</emphasis>
This is the first record of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="De Carlo" authorityYear="1938" box="[601,727,1679,1704]" class="Insecta" family="Belostomatidae" genus="Lethocerus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="27" pageNumber="478" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="maximus">
<emphasis box="[601,727,1679,1704]" italics="true" pageId="27" pageNumber="478">L. maximus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
from INR. This species was previously recorded from 
<collectingRegion country="Argentina" name="Corrientes" pageId="27" pageNumber="478">Corrientes Province</collectingRegion>
(
<bibRefCitation author="Armua de Reyes, A. C. &amp; Estevez, A. L." box="[265,641,1715,1742]" pageId="27" pageNumber="478" pagination="222 - 225" refId="ref45662" refString="Armua de Reyes, A. C. &amp; Estevez, A. L. (2016) Nuevos hallazgos de hemiptera (Belostomatidae) para la provincia de Corrientes, Argentina. Extensionismo, Innovacion y Transferencia Tecnologica, 3, 222 - 225. https: // doi. org / 10.30972 / eitt. 303023" type="journal article" year="2016">Armúa de Reyes &amp; Estévez 2016</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
